<template>
    <scroll class="cart-list" :data="[cartList]">
        <cart-list-item v-for="item in cartList" :key="item.iid" :item-info="item"></cart-list-item>
    </scroll>
</template>

<script>
import Scroll from 'components/common/srcoll/Scroll'
import CartListItem from './CartListItem.vue'

export default {
    name: "CartList",
    components: {
        Scroll,CartListItem
    },
    props: {
        cartList:{
            type: Array,
            default(){
                return []
            }
        }
    }
}
</script>

<style scoped>
    .cart-list{
        position: absolute;
        top: 44px;
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        bottom: 93px;
    }
</style>
